abstract: Clemson University, University of Alabama, University of Oklahoma and University of Iowa are top four in latest College Football Playoff selection committee rankings.
lead_paragraph: Clemson and Alabama remained No. 1 and No. 2, and Michigan State and Notre Dame were left just outside the top four in the latest set of rankings.

headline.main: Oklahoma and Iowa Enter Top 4 of College Football Playoff Rankings
headline.print_headline: Oklahoma and Iowa Make Move for Playoff
